chunk_content: 2 16 APPENDIX B: DQA OF NATIONAL AND PARTNER HIV TREATMENT AND PATIENT MONITORING SYSTEMS The following appendix is an excerpt from the “Data Quality Assessment of National and Partner HIV Treatment and Patient Monitoring Systems” implementation tool. This tool was developed in collaboration with WHO, UNAIDS, the Global Fund, and PEPFAR to ensure that there is one agreed upon methodology for conducting data quality assessments of treatment numbers.
